        {
            "Original": "The Responder takes the appropriate action based on the Request Message, and then publishes a Response Message to the Topic Name in the Response Topic property that was carried in the Request Message.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "4.",
            "Adjusted": "Step 4:"
        },
        {
            "Original": "In typical usage the Requester has subscribed to the Response Topic and thereby receives the Response Message.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "However, some other Client might be subscribed to the Response Topic in which case the Response Message will also be received and processed by that Client.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
